{"word":"H4405 - מִלָּה - millâh - mil-law' - Answer","slug":"H4405","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִלָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>millâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mil-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Answer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05DC;&#x05BC;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05DC;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - milla&#x0302;h  milleh</b> - <i>mil-law', mil-leh'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H4448\">H4448</a> (plural masculine as if from the second form); a <i>word</i>; collectively a <i>discourse</i>; figuratively a <i>topic: - </i> + answer, by-word, matter, any thing (what) to say, to speak (-ing), speak, talking, word."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4413\">H4413</a>, <a href=\"#/H4448\">H4448</a>, <a href=\"#/H4450\">H4450</a>"}]}